,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3449de1a8192a9858396233eccf6f26dca3f708c","tid":1816103,"uid":321834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:18:23.000Z","msg":"多謝勇武"},{"pid":"3cb818b1ba816b1a886061c0bd9de2e30e8794c3","tid":1816103,"uid":50880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3bfd1eed02d8096edca2bee331abdf4a7ce904a","tid":1816103,"uid":253223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"巴打有我同你齊上齊落 不中離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利伸無隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:26:06.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇隊唔駛灰，我果隊啲人都已經好習慣分頭單獨行動，始終冇可能次次同一位置，而且好易走散<br />\n<br />\n自己隊大半年黎唔算多人被捕，被捕左果啲都好好彩棄得切啲武器有機會打甩<br />\n<br />\n因為我地已經慣晒，二來最重要係危機意識，同埋做好隱藏身份嘅消毒措施<br />\n<br />\n入場離場冇cam就緊，而且場內一定包到實一實，我到今日仲見好多人淨係矇眼以下，髮型都仲係唔矇，其實咁樣已經好易被認被mark實"},{"pid":"81209361d47df19d4b97fb51339122af3210b93d","tid":1816103,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfcbd8e3f0fdd6408ac924e59749c53184f16338","tid":1816103,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"由得對家3毛自high<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"見到幾個post都話嗰D係真勇武<br />\n叫連登仔正視勇武退場嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fca011abe327ff9b61bff8bee5a950e4ca9b5f5","tid":1816103,"uid":34457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5c341c758995f43a0bb909843f7d4aefa06292c","tid":1816103,"uid":249639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:03:10.000Z","msg":"永不放棄<br />\n<br />\n多謝你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgm